text: Schafberg may refer to: *Schafberg (VS, Obergoms), a mountain range east of the Grimsel Pass in Switzerland *Schafberg (BE, Boltigen), a mountain peak in the Bernese Alps of Switzerland above Boltigen *Schafberg (Löbau), a mountain in Saxony, Germany *Schafberg (Ortler Alps), a mountain in the Ortler Alps on the border between Switzerland and Italy *Schafberg (Salzkammergut), a mountain in the Salzkammergut of Austria *Schafberg (Swabian Jura), a mountain in Baden-Württemberg, Germany *Schafberg (Vorarlberg), a mountain in the Alps in Vorarlberg, Austria
title: Schafberg
